        "content": "<p>vouillon requested <a href=\"https://github.com/orgs/bytecodealliance/teams/wasmtime-core-reviewers\">wasmtime-core-reviewers</a> for a review on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13450\">PR #13450</a>.</p>",
